Eike Batista  coal co. CCX says it
continues to invest in Colombia
*Co responds by e-mail to request for comment after Portafolio
reported it may halt Guajira project in Colombia
*CCX has invested about $500m in Colombia so far
*Says Guajira must be reviewed and adapted to market conditions
*Says Batista “believes” in project despite unfavorable market  To contact the reporter on this story:
